%section#wv-growing
  .shadow
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12
        %h1 growing
        %p Many of us struggle with the effects of the past - either things we've done which we wished we hadn’t, or things we've experienced through circumstances or relationships. God loves us and wants us to be free from the things that hold us back.
        %p Life groups and Sunday morning services are a great place to be prayed for. If you want to go deeper there are a variety of different options which are collectively called Streams of Hope.
    .row
      .col-md-3
        %h3 first stop
        %p
          Not sure where to start? Contact us for a First Stop appointment to discuss how you can best move forward.
      .col-md-3
        %h3 sozo
        %p
          Sozo is a powerful yet gentle prayer session that aims to deal with the things that are stopping you from connecting deeply with God.
      .col-md-3
        %h3 freedom in christ
        %p
          Freedom in Christ is a discipleship course that shows us who we are in Christ and how to live this out in day to day life.
      .col-md-3
        %h3 love after marriage
        %p
          Love After Marriage (LAM) is an 18 week course taking an in depth look at your relationship. It can revive and refresh your marriage, or help repair marriages that are struggling.
    .row
      .col-md-3
        %p
          %a{:href => 'mailto:enquiries@streamsofhope.org.uk'} Make an enquiry &raquo;
      .col-md-3
        %p
          %a{:href => '#wv-find-us'} Download the Sozo forms &raquo;
      .col-md-3
        %p
          %a{:href => 'mailto:enquiries@streamsofhope.org.uk?subject=Love After Marriage enquiry'} Register your interest &raquo;
      .col-md-3
        %p
