%section#wv-compassion
  .shadow
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12
        %h1 compassion
        %p We live out our faith by practically serving the needs of people in our city.
    .row
      .col-md-12
        %p.quote A recent visitor to our storehouse said, "I didn’t realise you did school uniform, my son goes to school looking like a ragamuffin. He hates it because he is embarrassed." She was overwhelmed to receive a new uniform for her son.
    .row
      .col-md-6
        %h3 children's storehouse
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/what-we-do/store-house.jpg'}
        %p
          We provide free good quality childrens clothes and equipment to those in need. We run a voucher system and accept referrals from statutory organisations across the area. Please get in touch if you need our services or want to donate 'as new' goods.
      .col-md-6
        %h3 foodbank
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/what-we-do/store-house.jpg'}
        %p
          Foodbank reaches out to serve those in need by providing a simple bag of groceries
        %p To get involved, grab a bag, fill a bag, give a bag! All you need to do is pick up a bag on a Sunday and bring it back full.
    .row
      .col-md-6
        %p
          %a{:href => '#'} Get in touch &raquo;
      .col-md-6
        %p
          %a{:href => '#'} Download a shopping list &raquo;
    .row
      .col-md-4
        %h3 karis kids
        %img{:src => '/images/kariskids.png'}
        %p
          Karis Kids is an initiative that integrates Ugandan children orphaned by AIDS into adoptive families. As a church we support the full time project leader, and we link families from church here with families in Uganda.
      .col-md-4
        %h3 street pastors
        %img{:src => '/images/streetpastors.jpg'}
        %p
          We support the Winchester Street Pastors scheme, joining with other local churches to send trained teams onto the streets at night from 9:30pm to 3:30am. We support vulnerable individuals and provide practical help.
      .col-md-4
        %h3 street team
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/what-we-do/street-teams.jpg'}
        %p
          On Saturday nights, a team goes out into Winchester city centre with soup, rolls, tea, coffee, blankets, socks, hats and a listening ear. We help those on the streets by providing for basic needs and giving them someone to talk to.
    .row
      .col-md-4
        %p
          %a{:href => 'http://kariskids.org.uk'} Visit the website &raquo;
      .col-md-4
        %p
          %a{:href => 'http://winchester.streepastors.org.uk'} Visit the website &raquo;
      .col-md-4
        %p
          %a{:href => 'admin@winvin.org.uk'} Get involved &raquo;


